### Add the named-accent variants

Append after the base `:root` block:

```css
/* Named-accent variants — light. Activate via <html data-accent="indigo|moss"> */
:root[data-accent="indigo"] {
  --accent: #1F2A55;
  --accent-rgb: 31, 42, 85;
}
:root[data-accent="moss"] {
  --accent: #2D4A2B;
  --accent-rgb: 45, 74, 43;
}
```

